Friends decompress on the quad, comparing responses from companies, particularly noting which ones responded warmly and discussing swag items like water bottles and phone chargers. A welcome announcement outlines the fair schedule over the PA system, while interview sign-up sheets fill with names, indicating ongoing interest in connecting with potential employers. A whiteboard lists employers who are scheduling same-day interviews, while career counselors redirect unsure students toward applicable industries, assisting them in navigating their career paths and reminding attendees to maintain eye contact. Workshops on networking etiquette begin in the adjoining classroom, and announcement chimes signal the final hour of the event.
